             * @return true

                function () use ($product, $newPrice): bool {

                    // Lock the row for update
                    $lockedProduct = Product::where('id', $product->id)->lockForUpdate()->firstOrFail();

                    $updated = $lockedProduct->update(['price' => $newPrice]);

                    if (! $updated) {
